quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  50,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  50,1,"q, qasam hai quran Majeed ki"
  50,2,"balkay inn logon ko taajjub is baat par howa ke aik khabardaar karne wala khud aِnhi mein se inn ke paas agaya phir munkareen kehnay lagey"" yeh to ajeeb baat hai"
  50,3,"kya jab hum mar jayen ge aur khaak ho jayen ge ( to dobarah uthaye jayen ge )? yeh wapsi to aqal se baeed hai """
  50,4,zameen un ke jism mein se jo kuch khati hai woh sab hamaray ilm mein hai aur hamaray paas aik kitaab hai jis mein sab kuch mehfooz hai
  50,5,balkay inn logon ne to jis waqt haq inn ke paas aaya usi waqt ussay saaf jhutla diya isi wajah se ab yeh uljan mein parre hue hain
  50,6,"acha, to kya unhon ne kabhi apne oopar aasman ki taraf nahi dekha? kis terhan hum ne usay banaya aur aaraasta kya, aur is mein kahin koi rakhna nahi hai"
  50,7,aur zameen ko hum ne bichhaya aur is mein pahar jamaye aur uss ke andar har terhan ki khush manzar nabataat uga den
  50,8,yeh saari cheeze ankhen kholnay wali aur sabaq dainay wali hain har uss bande ke liye jo ( haq ki taraf ) rujoo karne wala ho
  50,9,"aur aasman se hum ne barket wala pani nazil kya, phir is se baagh aur fasal ke ghallay"
  50,10,aur buland o baala khajoor ke darakht peda kar diye jin par phalon se lde hue khoshay teh Bar teh lagtay hain
  50,11,yeh intizam hai bundon ko rizaq dainay ka iss pani se hum aik murda zameen ko zindagi bakhash dete hain ( marey hue insanon ka zameen se ) niklana bhi isi terhan ho ga
  50,12,"inn se pehlay Nooh ki qoum, aur ashaab alras aur smod"
  50,13,"aur Aad , aur firaon, aur loot ke bhai"
  50,14,"aur ایکہ walay, aur tba ki qoum ke log bhi jhutla chuke hain har aik ne Rasolo-n ko jhtlaya, aur aakhir-kaar meri vayd unn par chaspan ho gayi"
  50,15,kya pehli baar ki takhleeq se hum aajiz thay? magar aik nai takhleeq ki taraf se yeh log shak mein parre hue hain
  50,16,hum ne ensaan ko peda kya hai aur is ke dil mein ubharnay walay waswason taq ko hum jantay hain hum is ki rug gardan se bhi ziyada uss se qareeb hain
  50,17,( aur hamaray is barah e raast ilm ke ilawa ) do katib is ke dayen aur baen baithy har cheez Sabt kar rahay hain
  50,18,koi lafz is ki zabaan se nahi nikalta jisay mehfooz karne ke liye aik haazir baash nigaran mojood nah ho
  50,19,"phir dekho, woh mout ki jaan kinny haq le kar aa pohanchi, yeh wohi cheez hai jis se to bhagta tha"
  50,20,"aur phir sor phonka gaya, yeh hai woh din jis ka tujhe khauf dilaya jata tha"
  50,21,har shakhs iss haal mein aa gaya ke uss ke sath aik haank kar laane wala hai aur aik gawahi dainay wala
  50,22,"iss cheez ki taraf se to ghaflat mein tha, hum ne woh parda hata diya jo tairay agay para howa tha aur aaj teri nigah khoob taiz hai"
  50,23,uss ke saathi ne arz kya yeh jo meri supurdagi mein tha haazir hai
  50,24,"hukum diya gaya"" pheink do jahannum mein har gatay(sarkash) kafir ko jo haq se inaad rakhta tha"
  50,25,"kher ko roknay wala aur hadd se tajawaz karne wala tha, shak mein para howa tha"
  50,26,"aur Allah ke sath kisi dosray ko khuda banaye betha tha daal do ussay sakht azaab mein """
  50,27,"uss ke saathi ne arz kya"" khudawanda, mein ne iss ko sarkash nahi banaya balkay yeh khud hi parlay darjay ki gumraahi mein para howa tha """
  50,28,"jawab mein irshad howa"" mere huzoor jhagra nah karo, mein tum ko pehlay hi injaam bad se khabardaar kar chuka tha"
  50,29,"mere haan baat palti nahi jati aur mein apne bundon par zulm tornay wala nahi hon """
  50,30,woh din jabkay hum jahannum se poucheen ge kya to bhar gayi? aur woh kahe gi kya aur kuch hai ?
  50,31,"aur jannat muttaqin ke qareeb le aayi jaye gi, kuch bhi daur nah hogi"
  50,32,"irshad hoga"" yeh hai woh cheez jis ka tum se wada kya jata tha, har uss shakhs ke liye jo bohat rujoo karne wala aur barri nighdasht karne wala tha"
  50,33,"jo be dekhe rehman se darta tha, aur jo dil garweedah liye hue aaya hai"
  50,34,"daakhil ho jao jannat mein salamti ke sath"" woh din hayaat abdi ka din hoga"
  50,35,"wahan un ke liye woh sab kuch hoga jo woh chahain ge, aur hamaray paas is se ziyada bhi bohat kuch un ke liye hai"
  50,36,hum un se pehlay bohat si qomon ko halaak kar chuke hain jo un se bohat ziyada taaqatwar theen aur duniya ke mulkon ko unhon ne chhaan mara tha phir kya woh koi jaye panah pa sakay ?
  50,37,"iss tareekh mein Ibrat ka sabaq hai har is shakhs ke liye jo dil rakhta ho, ya jo tavajja se baat ko sunay"
  50,38,hum ne zameen aur asmano ko aur unn ke darmain ki saari cheezon ko chay dinon mein peda kar diya aur hamein koi takan la-haq nah hui
  50,39,"pas ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, jo baatein yeh log banatay hain un par sabr karo, aur apne rab ki hamd ke sath is ki tasbeeh karte raho, tulu aftaab aur ghuroob aftaab se pehlay"
  50,40,aur raat ke waqt phir uss ki tasbeeh karo aur sajda raiziyun se farigh honay ke baad bhi
  50,41,"aur suno, jis din munaadi karne wala ( har shakhs ke ) qareeb hi se pukare ga"
  50,42,"jis din sab log Aawaz-ehashar ko theek theek sun rahay hon ge, woh zameen se mُrdon ke niklny ka din ho ga"
  50,43,"hum hi zindagi bkhshte hain aur hum hi mout dete hain, aur hamari taraf hi uss din sab ko palatna hai"
  50,44,jab zameen phatay gi aur log is ke andar se nikal kar taiz taiz bhage ja rahay hon ge yeh hashar hamaray liye bohat aasaan hai
  50,45,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, jo baatein yeh log bana rahay hain inhen hum khoob jantay hain, aur tumhara kaam un se jabran baat manwana nahi hai bas tum iss quran ke zareya se har uss shakhs ko nasiyaat kar do jo meri tanbeeh se daray"
